 2. The for loop is nested therefore you need to convert 2D indices to 1D. You are right: `x+y*width` would give you the correct array index, but in this case `width` is not the full width of your sketch in pixels but the width of the grid (i.e. the number of columns in the 4x4 grid: 4)
